title: Central Statistics Office Ireland, Number of Couples with No Children by Family Cycle by town, Ireland, 2006
name: Central Statistics Office Ireland, Number of Couples with No Children by Family Cycle by town, Ireland, 2006
description: This dataset has data on Number of Couples with No Children by Family Cycle throughout towns in Ireland that have a population of over 1000. The data includes numbers and percentages for the following age ranges: 0 to 4, 5 to 9, 10 to 14, 15 to 19, and 20 years and over. The towns have been geolocated by their lat/lon position. For more info about the data go to cso.ie/census.
